<h1>Privacy Policy for Salah Tracker</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2026</p>

<p>
Salah Tracker is a personal prayer tracking application. Your privacy is important to us.
This Privacy Policy explains how information is handled when you use the app.
</p>

<h2>Information Collection</h2>
<p>
Salah Tracker does <strong>not collect, store, or transmit any personal data</strong>.
</p>

<h2>Local Data Storage</h2>
<p>
All prayer tracking data is stored locally on your device only.
The app does not sync data to any server.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>
Salah Tracker does not use analytics, advertising services, or third-party tracking SDKs.
</p>

<h2>Permissions</h2>
<p>
Any permissions requested by the app are used solely to support app functionality
and are not used to collect personal information.
</p>

<h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>
Salah Tracker does not knowingly collect personal information from children.
</p>

<h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>
This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally. Any changes will be reflected on this page.
</p>

<h2>Contact Information</h2>
<p>
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact:
<br><br>
<strong>Email:</strong> mhasnuddin7@gmail.com
</p>

